        <h1>The Challenge with Genomic Data Visualization</h1>

        <p>Working with genomic data presents several significant challenges:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Multiple file formats (GFF, BED, FASTA) with different specifications</li>
            <li>Existing tools often crash with large datasets or require expensive licenses</li>
            <li>Comparing datasets across different sources is complex</li>
            <li>Creating publication-ready visualizations is time-consuming</li>
            <li>Collaboration requires identical software environments</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="highlight">
