        <ul>
            <li>Direct import of genomic files with automatic format detection</li>
            <li>Browser-based visualization requiring no software installation</li>
            <li>Handles stupidly large files without breaking</li>
            <li>Automated and manual feature grouping capabilities</li>
            <li>One-click export of publication-quality images</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="highlight">
