        <ul>
            <li>Chunked processing prevents memory overflow on large datasets</li>
            <li>IndexedDB for local data storage and caching</li>
            <li>Optimized rendering displays only visible regions</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Cross-platform compatibility:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Modern browser support with no installation requirements</li>
            <li>Vanilla JavaScript architecture for stability</li>
            <li>Canvas-based rendering for smooth performance</li>
        </ul>

